c: 6
v: 35
t: "And if their keeping away (from your message) is a great (disappointment) for you, then if you can, seek a tunnel in the earth or a ladder (to ascend) into the sky, then come to them with a sign (miracle, still they will not believe). And had God willed, He would have gathered all of them on guidance, so do not be of those who are ignorant"